Y'all ever notice
that cold spot in the hallway?

20:16.473 --> 20:17.117
Oh, yeah!

20:17.185 --> 20:19.286
That thing is <i>freezing!</i>

20:19.353 --> 20:21.453
You know what could learn
a lesson from that cold spot?

20:21.521 --> 20:24.690
The air conditioning unit
in my living room.

20:24.758 --> 20:26.959
Ladies and gentlemen,

20:27.027 --> 20:28.261
so yesterday, typical Sunday.

20:28.328 --> 20:29.328
I was hanging out
in my dreamatorium.

20:29.396 --> 20:30.696
Whoo!

20:30.764 --> 20:32.331
This ever happen to you guys?

20:32.399 --> 20:34.033
I couldn't remember
where I imagined the door.

20:35.235 --> 20:38.303
Then I realized I was in
an actual bathroom.

20:40.807 --> 20:42.640
Uh, no offense,
but this material

20:42.708 --> 20:44.609
seems pretty specific
to your apartment.

20:44.677 --> 20:46.845
I don't think it'll work
at an open mic.

20:52.217 --> 20:53.350
Y'all ever notice
the difference

20:53.418 --> 20:55.619
between me and Troy
brushing our teeth?

20:55.687 --> 20:58.722
I brush my teeth like this.

20:58.790 --> 21:01.658
Troy brushes his teeth
like this.

21:02.994 --> 21:04.061
I do!

21:04.129 --> 21:06.263
I do! I brush my teeth
just like that.

21:06.331 --> 21:07.977
Now you know what I'm gonna
talk about next.

21:08.097 --> 21:09.590
Toaster oven!

21:09.710 --> 21:11.156
It's from his album.

